pp.project_start_description: Welcome to the virtual experience of RE Society, Florida.

ep.ssml: Baywood is a new single-family home community located in sunny Florida City only 30 miles North of Florida city is Miami one of the country's most vibrant and culturally rich cities. Also nearby is the Miami International Airport, Walmart Supercenter, Aldi, Florida Keys Outlet Marketplace, numerous farmers markets and Florida's Turnpike, Florida city is adjacent to to national parks and the Florida Keys.
